nodes.name: Fungal infection
precautions: use detol or neem in bathing water

nodes.name: Gastroenteritis
precautions: stop eating solid food for while
try taking small sips of water

nodes.name: Cervical spondylosis
precautions: use heating pad or cold pack

nodes.name: Jaundice
precautions: eat fruits and high fiberous food

nodes.name: Varicose veins
precautions: lie down flat and raise the leg high

nodes.name: Psoriasis
precautions: wash hands with warm soapy water

nodes.name: Impetigo
precautions: soak affected area in warm water
remove scabs with wet compressed cloth
